Ninety-two articles including 55 guidelines, 2 policies, 5 journal articles, and 10 reports, as well as 19 patient information brochures from hospital websites were included for the review based on the inclusion criteria for the study. Policies and guidelines around HAI or IPC could not be located for Bangladesh and Indonesia despite further discussion with in-country partners for this study. One national guideline from Korea was retrieved for the review. 